{"id":31339,"date":"2024-01-30T01:50:00","date_gmt":"2022-01-29T20:20:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=31339"},"modified":"2022-11-30T14:40:48","modified_gmt":"2022-11-30T09:10:48","slug":"l-shaped-sectional-sofa","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/l-shaped-sectional-sofa\/","title":{"rendered":"L-Shaped Sectional Sofa Designs That Bring Luxury And Comfort To Your Living Room"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Expert tips on how to design your living room with a luxurious L-shaped sectional sofa&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When thinking about buying a sofa, we are usually a little sceptical about sectional sofas because of the space they take away. But sectional sofas are very comfortable and come with unique space-saving options. It is a great option if you have a big family or have friends coming over to your place frequently. So, here we bring to you some smart L-shaped sectional sofa designs that will lend a cosy vibe to your home and help you enjoy your movie nights or happening parties with your friends and family. Read along to know more.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. An L-Shaped Sectional Sofa With Chaise To Match Your Industrial-Style Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Industrial-style living rooms are gaining huge popularity because of their rugged and bold look. This living room is designed with an L-shaped sectional sofa in faux leather for extra comfort. The grey gypsum wall on one side and the brick cladding wall on the other create the perfect combination to elevate the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/living-room-design\/\">living room interiors<\/a>. You can add a statement timepiece on the wall to accentuate the space. Add some track lights, an accent lamp and a floor carpet to make the living room look warm and welcoming. This sofa also comes with an attached chaise section to rest your legs and lounge on it after a hard day at work.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31173059\/an-shaped-sectional-sofa-with-chaise-to-match-your-industrial-style-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"An l shaped sectional sofa with chaise to match your industrial-style living room\" data-id=\"31342\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31173059\/an-shaped-sectional-sofa-with-chaise-to-match-your-industrial-style-living-room.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31342\" class=\"wp-image-31342\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31173059\/an-shaped-sectional-sofa-with-chaise-to-match-your-industrial-style-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31173059\/an-shaped-sectional-sofa-with-chaise-to-match-your-industrial-style-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31173059\/an-shaped-sectional-sofa-with-chaise-to-match-your-industrial-style-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31173059\/an-shaped-sectional-sofa-with-chaise-to-match-your-industrial-style-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">A warm living room with a leather L-shaped sofa<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. A Small L-Shaped Sectional Sofa For Compact Living Rooms<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you desire a sectional sofa but are worried that it might make your small living room look cluttered, this small L-shaped sectional sofa design is for you. This three-seater L-shaped sectional sofa with a chaise unit can couple into a comfortable bed. The sleek coffee table and side table combination add to the room\u2019s aesthetics and functionality. You can decorate the walls with some colourful wallpaper to add a vibrance to your living room. Install cove lights on the false ceiling and some pendant lights to light up your living room and create an illusion of a bigger space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174038\/a-small-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-for-compact-living-rooms.jpg\" alt=\"A small l shaped sectional sofa for compact living rooms with a chaise\" data-id=\"31343\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174038\/a-small-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-for-compact-living-rooms.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31343\" class=\"wp-image-31343\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174038\/a-small-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-for-compact-living-rooms.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174038\/a-small-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-for-compact-living-rooms-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174038\/a-small-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-for-compact-living-rooms-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174038\/a-small-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-for-compact-living-rooms-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">A small L-shaped sectional sofa with a chaise<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. A Double Sided L-Shaped Sectional Sofa To Lounge With Your Friends And Family<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This double-sided L-shaped sectional sofa in white and teal is apt for a spacious living room. It provides ample sitting space and can be used as a bed when required. Opt for light colours on the walls and sheer curtains to bring in ample natural light. Add some indoor plants to the space for a dash of freshness. This L-shaped sectional sleeper sofa is perfect for enjoying movie nights with your friends and family.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174257\/a-double-sided-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-to-lounge-with-your-friends-and-family.jpg\" alt=\"A double sided l shaped sectional sofa to lounge with your friends and family\" data-id=\"31344\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174257\/a-double-sided-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-to-lounge-with-your-friends-and-family.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31344\" class=\"wp-image-31344\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174257\/a-double-sided-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-to-lounge-with-your-friends-and-family.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174257\/a-double-sided-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-to-lounge-with-your-friends-and-family-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174257\/a-double-sided-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-to-lounge-with-your-friends-and-family-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174257\/a-double-sided-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-to-lounge-with-your-friends-and-family-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. A Modern L-Shaped Sectional Sofa With Yellow Accents To Add Some Vibrance<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Grey adds an edge to your home interiors and infuses an elegant vibe. But if the colour seems too dull for you, add some pop colours in your living room with a yellow accent chair and some pillows. The yellow shade helps break the monotony of grey and adds a fun element to the decor. You can dress the floor with a big checkered carpet. The trick to designing a living room with large L-shaped sectional sofas is to opt for clean lines, simple designs and minimal accents. This will help bring attention to your luxurious L-shaped sectional sofa and make it the show stopper of your home interiors.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-4 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174506\/an-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-with-yellow-accents-to-add-some-vibrance.jpg\" alt=\"An l shaped sectional sofa with yellow accents to add some vibrance\" data-id=\"31345\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174506\/an-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-with-yellow-accents-to-add-some-vibrance.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31345\" class=\"wp-image-31345\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174506\/an-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-with-yellow-accents-to-add-some-vibrance.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174506\/an-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-with-yellow-accents-to-add-some-vibrance-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174506\/an-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-with-yellow-accents-to-add-some-vibrance-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174506\/an-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-with-yellow-accents-to-add-some-vibrance-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Add colourful accents to a grey L-shaped sofa<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. A Living Room Designed With A Large L-Shaped Sectional Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A light purple hue brings in a soft and cosy touch to your living room and sets a romantic tone for your home. You can use cream coloured L-shaped sectional sofa covers to match the pastel purple hue on the wall. Add a designer light fixture, some cove lights and spotlights to illuminate the room. We have added a wooden partition unit to bring some warmth to the living room while creating a subtle divider. The clear glass door brings in a lot of natural light while letting you enjoy the outside view as you chill on your luxuriously large L-shaped sectional sofa.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-5 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174653\/a-living-room-designed-with-a-large-l-shaped-sectional-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"A living room designed with a large l shaped sectional sofa while lounging on this comfy sofa\" data-id=\"31346\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174653\/a-living-room-designed-with-a-large-l-shaped-sectional-sofa.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=31346\" class=\"wp-image-31346\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174653\/a-living-room-designed-with-a-large-l-shaped-sectional-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174653\/a-living-room-designed-with-a-large-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174653\/a-living-room-designed-with-a-large-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/31174653\/a-living-room-designed-with-a-large-l-shaped-sectional-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Enjoy the view while lounging on this comfy sofa<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope you enjoyed reading about L-shaped sectional sofa units and want to incorporate them in your living room as well. Now, book a free consultation with our expert designers and they will help you design your living room with style and panache. From space-saving units, extra storage space to stylish furniture and finishes like these, our personalised design solutions will have you covered. And for more such exciting interior design ideas, check out our blog and guide section now.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Do you want a living room that is lively and livable\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02171514\/living-room-lively-livable.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>If you enjoyed reading about L shaped sectional sofa designs, also explore <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/different-sofa-styles-for-your-home\/\">different sofa style designs for your home<\/a>.<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Dreamy Interiors That Spell 'WOW'<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our de